59, \"to\": 3379}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If we are achieving the same medals as London, I think that's a hugely successful Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 3381, \"to\": 3471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3421, \"end\": 3427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.205845231059828e-12, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same medals\", \"from\": 3402, \"to\": 3417}, {\"ngram\": \"a hugely successful Games\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Medals or moments, what comes first?\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3509, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Medals\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3479}, {\"ngram\": \"moments\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For those who fund our sport then their millions of public money demands a return on investment measured in gold, silver and bronze.\", \"from\": 3510, \"to\": 3642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3538}, {\"ngram\": \"their millions\", \"from\": 3544, \"to\": 3558}, {\"ngram\": \"public money\", \"from\": 3562, \"to\": 3574}, {\"ngram\": \"a return\", \"from\": 3583, \"to\": 3591}, {\"ngram\": \"investment\", \"from\": 3595, \"to\": 3605}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3618, \"to\": 3622}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3630}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 3635, \"to\": 3641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But no-one watching at home is losing any sleep that Team GB got a few less gold medals than Australia, France or the Netherlands.\", \"from\": 3644, \"to\": 3774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3697, \"end\": 3704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999998873713657, \"rank\": 1.1261924880196964e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/T